column5: Got this boat last year used and it has 2 fasteners secured that I assume are for bumpers. Can’t seem to find the matching connectors online (getting old). If anyone uses them and can point me in the right direction I’d appreciate it. Thx.
I suspect, the swivel keys either got broken or the previous owner took them off for some reason.
Would a knot on the end of a rope work?
Looks like a easy enough piece to make but might be better served to just replace with full sets. Thx guys.
I suspect the swivel keys are attached to the bumpers
